sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as SearchUser
participant UI as DashboardSearchModal
participant Fetcher as DashboardSearchFetcher
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant Org as OrganizationApi
participant Friend as FriendApi
participant Chat as MessageApi
participant Task as TaskMeetingApis
participant NotifyDoc as NotificationDocumentApis
User->>UI: Nhap tu khoa va chon tab
UI->>Fetcher: fetchDashboardSearchResults(query,scope)
Fetcher->>Fetcher: debounce + validate context(orgId/friendId)
par Org data
  Fetcher->>Gateway: GET /api/organizations/my
  Gateway->>Org: proxy
and Friend data
  Fetcher->>Gateway: GET /api/friends
  Gateway->>Friend: proxy
and Chat data
  Fetcher->>Gateway: GET /api/messages/search or DM search
  Gateway->>Chat: proxy
and Task/Meeting
  Fetcher->>Gateway: GET /api/tasks + /api/meetings
  Gateway->>Task: proxy
and Notification/Document
  Fetcher->>Gateway: GET /api/notifications + /api/documents
  Gateway->>NotifyDoc: proxy
end
alt Du context va co data
  Fetcher->>UI: merge + normalize + render cards
else Thieu context/loi tung nhanh
  Fetcher->>UI: render warning row theo nhom loi
end
